de.interactive_instruments.etf.testdriver

Interface TestDriver

  • All Superinterfaces:
    de.interactive_instruments.Configurable, de.interactive_instruments.Initializable, de.interactive_instruments.Releasable

    public interface TestDriver
extends de.interactive_instruments.Configurable, de.interactive_instruments.Releasable
    Test Driver Encapsulates a test engine, manages test engine specific Executable Test Suites and defines the main entry point for executing Test Suites against an Test Object.
